  "text": "Since there are no Majorana fermions in 3 Euclidean dimensions we switch to Minkowskispace with metric tensor η µν = diag(1, −1, −1) and γ-matrices γ µ = (σ 2 , iσ 3 , iσ 1 ), where µ = 0, 1, 2. After setting up the flow equation we return to Euclidean space, see [CITATION_1] . With the above definitions we are able to construct the off-shell supersymmetric action in R 1,2 superspace:",
